name: spysystem/mydhl
description: Welcome to the official DHL Express APIs (MyDHL API) below are the published API Documentation to fulfill your shipping needs with DHL Express.  Please follow the process described [here](https://developer.dhl.com/api-reference/dhl-express-mydhl-api#get-started-section/user-guide--get-access) to request access to the DHL Express - MyDHL API services    In case you already have DHL Express - MyDHL API Service credentials please ensure to use the endpoints/environments listed  [here](https://developer.dhl.com/api-reference/dhl-express-mydhl-api#get-started-section/user-guide--environments)
